467
00:48:12,052 --> 00:48:14,646
O que você faz se algo
ruim acontece?

468
00:48:14,722 --> 00:48:16,155
Chamo a mamãe.

469
00:48:17,391 --> 00:48:19,359
Certo.

470
00:48:54,158 --> 00:48:56,319
